00:18:47.752 --> 00:18:51.047 position:50% align:center
♪ would he always be lonely? ♪

00:18:51.131 --> 00:18:53.675 position:50% align:center
♪ "You are not alone," ♪

00:18:53.758 --> 00:18:58.972 position:50% align:center
♪ said a spring breeze
passing by ♪

