00:19:23.329 --> 00:19:25.623 position:50% align:center
♪ SO LA TI DO SO ♪

00:19:25.707 --> 00:19:32.130 position:50% align:center
♪ sings the little bird
now as it flies ♪

00:19:33.506 --> 00:19:36.676 position:50% align:center
[ALL chuckle]

00:19:36.760 --> 00:19:40.805 position:50% align:center
Amazing! When did you have
time to learn my song?

00:19:40.889 --> 00:19:42.390 position:50% align:center
I've always loved this one.

00:19:42.474 --> 00:19:44.559 position:50% align:center
[BOTH laugh]

00:19:44.642 --> 00:19:48.021 position:50% align:center
There's the beautiful smiling
sister I've been missing.

00:19:48.104 --> 00:19:49.689 position:50% align:center
I've missed your smile, too!

00:19:49.773 --> 00:19:52.984 position:50% align:center
It's so good to have
you back again.

00:19:55.403 --> 00:19:58.782 position:50% align:center
And now, I'd like to
share a brand-new song.

00:19:58.865 --> 00:20:00.116 position:50% align:center
It's about love.

00:20:00.200 --> 00:20:03.995 position:50% align:center
For everyone who's ever
loved anyone or anything.

00:20:11.586 --> 00:20:15.382 position:50% align:center
♪ Tender little twins
budding up toward the sky ♪

00:20:15.465 --> 00:20:20.220 position:50% align:center
♪ Where the garden
grows in the dew ♪

00:20:20.303 --> 00:20:24.099 position:50% align:center
♪ Colors from within soon
